/**
 * @defgroup osal_env_api osal_env API
 * @ingroup osal_family_group
 *
 * @brief Low-level OSAL environment abstraction.
 *
 * @details
 * The `osal_env` module provides portable low-level environment access
 * primitives through the Operating System Abstraction Layer.
 *
 * It is responsible for environment-related queries only and is not intended
 * to act as a configuration system, persistence layer, or high-level runtime
 * service.
 */
